  <brief_title>Manual Versus Targer-controll Infusion in Reduction of Awareness and Dreaming</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reduction of Awareness and Dreaming During Neurosurgical Procedures Using Target- Controlled Infusion, Comparison With Manual Total Intravenous Anesthesia TIVA.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
