    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Glasgow Coma scale 15

          -  ASA Physical Status Classification System I - III

          -  planed surgery for brain tumor to 5 hours

          -  postoperative awakening

        Exclusion Criteria:

